data.description: Welcome Home to your new home with plenty of room for those large families and/or to entertain and host dinner parties or game nights? This 5 bedroom, 2.5 bath with a walk way that over looks the main living area, does not disappoint. With an abundance of stone accents throughout, to include the fireplace and breakfast bar, this home is a true showstopper. The kitchen is equipped with a walk in pantry, beautiful breakfast bar, granite counter tops built by Vale-Irvin Homes.  In the master you will find a large walk-in closet to help keep those shopping trip finds organized. Outside is a covered patio and privacy fence to help make back yard entertaining more pleasant. These are just a few of the amenities you will find with this home. Located close to many local shopping and entertainment areas as well as Fort Cavazos, this home is perfect for someone relocating, a large family or someone looking for an upgrade. This home won’t last long so schedule your private viewing today.
